claim.claim-text:
5. A method for operating the timer device according to claim 1, comprising the following steps:
set a first time period to be counted by a first timer;
set a second time period to be counted by a second timer, said second time period being a portion of the first time period;
when said second time period is expired, but said first time period is not expired, the second timer begins again the measure of the second time period; and
when said second time period is expired and said first time period is also expired, control means of the timer device are reset, and a component connected with the timer device starts a new operation cycle.
